{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1701z–17","heading":"Increasing access and understanding of energy efficient mortgages","label":"1701z–17 Increasing access and understanding of energy efficient mortgages","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1701z–17","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/ch13","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1701z%E2%80%9317","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Foreclosure Prevention Act of 2008, and also as part of the Housing and Economic Recovery Act of 2008, and not as part of the National Housing Act which comprises this chapter."],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definition","label":"a Definition","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1701z–17/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1701z–17","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1701z%E2%80%9317%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"As used in this section, the term “energy efficient mortgage” has the same meaning as given that term in paragraph (24) of .section 12704 of title 42","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Recommendations to eliminate barriers to use of energy efficient mortgages","label":"b Recommendations to eliminate barriers to use of energy efficient mortgages","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1701z–17/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1701z–17","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1701z%E2%80%9317%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1701z–17/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1701z–17/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.go